    #workspace
      #instructions        
          h2 Instructions
          ul
            li #[a(href="https://www.google.com/search?q=turn+off+enhance+pointer+precision" target="blank") Make sure that "Enhance pointer precision" is off].
            li Update the "in-game sensitivity" to your preference.
            li Pick a weapon, mag size, and attachment level.
            li Click anywhere on the area below.
            li Get a high score by compensating a recoil.
          p Enable "Show path" to see the ideal compensation trajectory.
          p Enable "Show pacer" to see a running dot to follow ("show path" is on).
          p 
            i I recommend starting with "show pacer" on, then with only "show path" and then, as a final test - with both options off.
          p Enable "Real trace" to use one of the real recorded traces instead of a fixed average.
          p Scores are counted separately for different setups.
          p #[a#dismiss-instructions(href="#") Dismiss instructions]
      #stage